About VibEats

Finding great food should be exciting, not overwhelming.

VibEats is a modern restaurant discovery app that helps food lovers discover amazing places to eat, rate their experiences with the exclusive BiteMeter™, and share their favorite meals with friends.

Whether you are searching for a hidden taco truck, the perfect brunch spot, an incredible coffee shop, or the newest restaurant in town, VibEats helps you discover places worth visiting.

Unlike traditional review apps that rely on generic star ratings, VibEats introduces BiteMeter™—a fresh, visual way to capture how every dining experience truly felt.

Every meal has a story. Every bite has a vibe.

⸻

